signs.text: Tread carefully of what lies ahead.
One shouldn't venture alone in these caves.
In memory of Azaria,my dearest friend.
Here lies R,a bittersweet memory,at peace.
A path may open once the lord of ogres perishes.
An ancient warrior carrying a forgotten weapon.
The Queen's death will open a path.
Turn back now,or bring an army.
A graveyard created to come to peace., With all of it.
This rock was used to test tile rotations.,I now refuse to remove it.
